text: Kaadu sinni buxaaxil daffeya, caagid maliinoh mawqinaay, sinni bilqaa kee qax-maqaané marin labha maybulliina naharsi jaahiliyyah agbi kah aybullak suge innah islaamaninnak duma. Kaadu salat soolisaay, zaká acuwaay, Yallaa kee kay farmoytih amri oggola. Kee Nabii buxah maraw cagalah Yalli dambii kee umaané siinik kalaah saytunnoysiyyah sin saytunnoysam faxak
